<item>
            <title>[LU-15957] LNet: add latency stats to lnet_selftest output </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15957</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Although lnet_selftest is able to run &quot;ping&quot; tests (vs. &quot;brw&quot;), it doesn&apos;t appear to be collecting and reporting any data useful for analysing network latency.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Use this ticket for tracking activities on adding network latency data collection and stats reporting to lnet_selftest.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
